Example 3e - Input value of a primitive data type (constant integer or array of integers, wrapped in a JSON object).SELECT PAIRS({"name" : 3});
Result: [ { "$1": [ [ "name", 3 ] ] } ]
SELECT PAIRS({"name" : [1,2,3]});
